creator: ReviveLtd
descriptionHtml:
Revive is the the funny photo animation app
Revive is a super easy AI app that lets you create an animation from any photo. You don’t need editing skills or have to spend time learning. Just one tap and any image can sing or speak.
Revive makes any boring photo weird and fun. Start a conversation in a messenger, get comments on social media, or illustrate an opinion with a Revive video.

Animate photo with a face in it for an instant comic effect. Edit sketches, comics, a meme or pictures with the animation creator. Bring pictures to life.

How does Revive work?
- Upload a photo
- Pick a sound you want it to sing or say
- Tap Revive and make a photo sing and dance.
- Share it with your friends on social media

Here's what you can do with Revive:
Use the photo animator to bring images to life and share them with the world.
Add a live photo instead of a regular one to your profile.
Revive is the perfect animation maker for classic art portraits with a persona on it.

Types of Revive sounds:
- Hit songs
Make your own photo, your kid’s photo, or your best friend’s selfie sing rock hits, pop music classics, or karaoke favorites that fit their personality the best.
- Meme sounds
Animate your photos to viral video hits and post the hilarious results to jump on a trend. There’s no need to take a video, just Revive.
- Quotes from movies and TV shows
Now your baby can sound like Don Corleone, your lazy cat can say "Love me, feed me, never leave me" as Garfield, and your ex can promise you “I’ll be back” as Terminator. Pick a phrase that suits the image and creates a funny combo.

New songs, sounds, and lines are added daily.
----

In case of any questions, issues, or collaboration requests, contact us at hi@reviveapp.net

Terms and Conditions: https://reviveapp.net/terms/
Privacy Policy: https://reviveapp.net/privacy-policy/
